Vulois

Vulois opened the entrance to his mountain, and saw the three bots.

"Hello, I am Vulois. If you truly wish to join, than you must come 
with me so I may evaluate you. So you must all stay close to me so 
you do not get lost in the tunnels and.." Vulois paused as he saw 
Dark Prime. He could feel the negative energy reeling off him.

"Why have you come? Are you another of Nemesis' cronies doing his 
dirty work? Haven't all of you realized that the power of the Matrix 
will defeat evil always? Begon from this place, before my powers 
smite you!"
